---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: "faqs.html"
page_key: faqs
title: "FAQs — Meghan &amp; Owen"
description: "The questions you're about to ask: the Friday timing, dress code, kids, plus-ones, getting to Whitehouse Station, parking, and more."
---

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="page-hero__row">
        <div data-reveal>
          <p class="kicker">Good questions</p>
          <h1 class="h-lg mt-m">Everything you’re about to ask.</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="lede muted" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">We’d rather answer the question before you have to ask it. Here’s the short version; if we’ve missed something, just reach out — we’d love to hear from you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell">
      {%- for g in faqs %}
      <div class="faq-group" data-reveal>
        <p class="subhead">{{ g.subhead }}</p>
        {%- for q in g.items %}
        <details class="faq"{% if q.open %} open{% endif %}>
          <summary>{{ q.question | mdInline | safe }}<span class="ic" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            {{ q.answer | md | safe }}
            {%- if q.voices %}
            <div class="voices">
              {%- for v in q.voices %}
              <div class="voice"><span class="who{% if v.owen %} is-owen{% endif %}">{{ v.who }}</span><p>{{ v.text }}</p></div>
              {%- endfor %}
            </div>
            {%- endif %}
          </div>
        </details>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}

      <div class="text-center mt-l" data-reveal>
        <p class="h-sm center measure" style="max-width:28ch;">Still wondering about something?</p>
        <p class="muted mt-s center measure" style="max-width:40ch;">Reach out anytime at <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact_email }}">{{ site.contact_email }}</a> — we promise a real and quick reply.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
